longBusinessSummary: Zhong Nong Yuan Fang Holdings, Inc. manufactures and distributes supplements and all-natural remedies that are alternatives to prescription drugs. Its products include Focamine, an all-natural focus, attention, and concentration promoter for people suffering from ADHD; and Sombium, an alternative sleep aid. The company was formerly known as Alternaturals, Inc. and changed its name to Zhong Nong Yuan Fang Holdings, Inc. in December 2021. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Grandville, Michigan.
